title: Jimmy Butler Reigns As the Heat Take Game 3 of the NBA Finals | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja convene right after Game 3 of the NBA Finals to talk about the Lakers’ meltdown and Jimmy Butler’s unreal 40-point triple-double (0:41). Then they each crown their Real One of the Week (37:58).

Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
